description: This source file contains backend APIs for managing IP interfaces, including CRUD operations for IP interface objects and their properties within the COSA Data Model for a CPE device. It includes functions to get/set parameters, validate configurations, commit or rollback changes, and manage IP interface instances and their associated IPv4 addresses.

methods.name: BOOL IP_GetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL * pBool)
methods.description: Retrieves Boolean parameters such as IPv4Capable, IPv6Capable, IPv4Enable, IPv6Enable.

methods.name: BOOL IP_GetParamIntValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,int * pInt)
methods.description: Retrieves Integer parameters (not used in current code).

methods.name: BOOL IP_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters like IPv4Status, IPv6Status.

methods.name: ULONG IP_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
BOOL IP_SetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL bValue)
methods.description: Sets Boolean parameters such as IPv4Enable, IPv6Enable (not supported for some).

methods.name: BOOL IP_SetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG uValue)
methods.description: Sets ULONG parameters including MaxMTUSize, TTL, ArpCacheTimeout.

methods.name: BOOL IP_SetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pString)
methods.description: Sets string parameters such as ULAPrefix (not supported currently).

methods.name: BOOL IP_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * pReturnParamName,ULONG * puLength)
methods.description: Validates the entire IP configuration before commit.

methods.name: ULONG IP_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits the IP configuration changes to the backend.

methods.name: ULONG IP_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back the IP configuration to previous state on failure.

methods.name: ULONG Interface2_GetEntryCount(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Returns the count of IP Interface instances.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE Interface2_GetEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG nIndex,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Retrieves a specific IP Interface entry by index.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE Interface2_AddEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Adds a new IP Interface instance.

methods.name: ULONG Interface2_DelEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ANSC_HANDLE hInstance)
methods.description: Deletes an existing IP Interface instance.

methods.name: BOOL Interface2_GetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL * pBool)
methods.description: Retrieves boolean parameters of IP Interface such as Enable, Loopback, AutoIPEnable, IPv4Enable, IPv6Enable.

methods.name: BOOL Interface2_GetParamIntValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,int * pInt)
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameters of IP Interface (not implemented).

methods.name: BOOL Interface2_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters of IP Interface such as Status, LastChange, MaxMTUSize, Type, TTL, and IPv6 related parameters.

methods.name: ULONG Interface2_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters for IP Interface including Alias, Name, LowerLayers, Router.

methods.name: Interface2_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean parameters for IP Interface such as Enable, Loopback, AutoIPEnable, UpnpIgdEnabled.

methods.name: Interface2_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets integer parameters for IP Interface (not implemented).

methods.name: Interface2_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets ULONG parameters such as MaxMTUSize, TTL, ArpCacheTimeout.

methods.name: Interface2_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters of IP Interface like Alias, LowerLayers, Router.

methods.name: Interface2_Validate
methods.description: Validates the interface configuration before commit to avoid conflicts like duplicate alias.

methods.name: ULONG Interface2_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits the interface configuration changes to the backend, adding new entries if needed.

methods.name: Interface2_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back uncommitted changes to previous known good configuration.

methods.name: ULONG IPv4Address_GetEntryCount(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Counts IPv4 Address entries associated with an IP interface.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE IPv4Address_GetEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG nIndex,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Retrieves an IPv4 Address entry by index.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE IPv4Address_AddEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Adds a new IPv4 Address entry to an IP interface.
